name: Sanshu Inu (OLD)
description: Sanshu inu is a deflationary community based meme token which rewards holders on every transaction. We are constantly growing and making new memes to create a fun and friendly environment in our telegram. This is what we think will make us stand out from the rest of the ETH dogs.
